"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-04-12-2000-foreign-troops-help-france-secure-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP)- Some 2,000 foreign troops and police will be sent to Paris to bolster security for this summer's Olympic Games as France remains on high alert following attack threats, the French armed forces minister said Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"score\": 0.971579111471086, \"rank\": 0.02589170294381642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999824810858, \"rank\": 1.7518887752230674e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"score\": 0.971579111471086, \"rank\": 0.02589170294381642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"Some 2,000 foreign troops\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 57}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"following attack threats\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"the French armed forces minister\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have something like 2,000 foreign police officers, gendarmes and troops who will be joining the protection system for the Olympic Games,\\\" Sebas